<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10147051>
    dc:description "FIGURE 41. Humeral processes of Eutegaeoidea. Eutegaeidae: (a) Eutegaeus soror P. Balogh, 1985; (b) Atalotegaeus mensarosi J. & P. Balogh, 1983a; (c) Neseutegaeus latus Hammer, 1966; (d); Humerotegaeus concentricus gen. et sp. nov.; Neoeutegaeidae fam. nov.: (e) Neoeutegaeus melipsilon sp. nov.; Compactozetidae: (f) Compactozetes rotoruensis Hammer, 1966; (g) Hamotegeus longiseta P. Balogh, 1986; (h) Sadocepheus tohokuensis Fujikawa, 2003; Bornebuschiidae fam. nov.: (i) Bornebuschia peculiaris Hammer, 1966; (j) Dicrotegaeus mirabilis Luxton, 1988b; Pterozetidae: (k) Pterozetes lawrencei sp. nov.; (l) Dudichella membranigera Balogh, 1970; Porrhotegaeidae fam. nov.: (m) Porrhotegaeus ornatus J. Balogh & Mahunka, 1966; Cerocepheidae: (n) Cerocepheus osornensis Ermilov, 2020." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10147051/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10147055>
    dc:description "FIGURE 43. Lateral margin of coxisternum of Eutegaeoidea viewed in ventral aspect, showing pedotectum I (pd I) and II (pd II) and discidium (di). Eutegaeidae:(a) Eutegaeusodontatus sp. nov.; (b) Atalotegaeus monteithi (J. & P.Balogh, 1983b) comb. nov.; (c) Neseutegaeus wardi sp. nov.; (d) Humerotegaeus concentricus gen. et sp. nov.; Neoeutegaeidae fam. nov.: (e) Neoeutegaeus torsteini sp. nov.; Compactozetidae: (f) Compactozetes bundjalung sp. nov.; (g) Hamotegeus granulatus J. Balogh & Mahunka 1969; (h) Sadocepheus remus sp. nov.; Bornebuschiidae fam. nov.: (i) Bornebuschia binodosa Luxton, 1988b; (j) Dicrotegaeus incurvus Ermilov and Minor, 2015; Pterozetidae: (k) Pterozetes lawrencei sp. nov.; (l) Dudichella membranigera Balogh, 1970; Porrhotegaeidae fam. nov.: (m) Porrhotegaeus ornatus J. Balogh & Mahunka, 1966; Cerocepheidae: (n) Cerocepheus osornensis Ermilov, 2020." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10147055/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10147053>
    dc:description "FIGURE 42. Lamellae of Eutegaeoidea. Eutegaeidae: (a) Eutegaeus soror P. Balogh, 1985; (b) Atalotegaeus monteithi (J. & P. Balogh, 1983b) comb. nov.; (c) Neseutegaeus latus Hammer, 1966; (d) Humerotegaeus concentricus gen. et sp. nov.; Neoeutegaeidae fam. nov.: (e) Neoeutegaeus malcolmi sp. nov.; Compactozetidae: (f) Compactozetes bundjalung sp. nov.; (g) Hamotegeus longiseta P. Balogh, 1986; (h) Sadocepheus tohokuensis Fujikawa, 2003; Bornebuschiidae fam. nov.: (i) Bornebuschia peculiaris Hammer, 1966; (j) Dicrotegaeus mirabilis Luxton, 1988b; Pterozetidae: (k) Pterozetes lawrencei sp. nov.; (l) Dudichella membranigera Balogh, 1970; Porrhotegaeidae fam. nov.: (m) Porrhotegaeus ornatus J. Balogh & Mahunka, 1966; Cerocepheidae: (n) Cerocepheus osornensis Ermilov, 2020." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10147053/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

